title: This Ex-Roadie Is Weaving Magic In Her Instagram Photos
text:
Swagata Dam Mar . 31 . 2017 Remember Suzanna Mukherjee from the sixth season of MTV Roadies ? Well, I just happened to come across her Instagram profile today and I must say, she looks rather gorgeous in her pictures. The half Bengali and half Russian pretty lass is now an actress. Here are some of her photos.
